               "text": "### Images from Ashmolean\n\nThese images are copyright for Ashmolean and allowed to be used according to the license determined by them.\n\nTo visualize all images, use the left and right arrows on the slide below.",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p><div class=\"htSlides\"><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">1 / 4</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgEA\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgEA', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Fragment of the epic <i>Enmerkar and the lord of Aratta</i>. © Ashmolean Museum, University of Oxford (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillPrimarySource('434e68bc-6ee5-4b45-8692-beb26bd9da7f'); return false;\"><i>Ashmolean Image Library</i></a>).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">2 / 4</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgHarappaW\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgHarappaW', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Harappa Seal. © Ashmolean Museum, University of Oxford (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillPrimarySource('1696d647-d450-44e3-9067-18aac69bce3d'); return false;\"><i>Ashmolean Museum Oxford, 11/30/2024</i></a>). Shared under the <a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/\" target=\"_blank\">Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 International (CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 license.</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">3 / 4</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgS\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgS', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Estatuillas of the Sixth Dynasty. © Ashmolean Museum, University of Oxford (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillPrimarySource('f3b5c752-03d2-446d-b398-2c7f3ad4c2ee'); return false;\"><i>Ashmolean Image Library, 01/02/2025</i></a>).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">4 / 4</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgKL\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgKL', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Sumerian King List. © Ashmolean Museum, University of Oxford (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillPrimarySource('4d0b579d-57af-45e1-87b0-d402dd778968'); return false;\"><i>Ashmolean Image Library, 02/01/2024</i></a>).</div></div><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-left htSlidePrev\" onclick=\"htPlusDivs(-1);\"></i><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-right htSlideNext\" onclick=\"htPlusDivs(1);\"></i></div></p>",
               "source": null,
