            },
            {
               "text": "### Image Descriptions\n- **Slide 1 / 4**: Fragment of the epic *Enmerkar and the lord of Aratta*. © Ashmolean Museum, University of Oxford (*Ashmolean Image Library*).\n- **Slide 2 / 4**: Harappa Seal. © Ashmolean Museum, University of Oxford (*Ashmolean Museum Oxford, 11/30/2024*). Shared under the Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 International (CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 license.\n- **Slide 3 / 4**: Estatuillas of the Sixth Dynasty. © Ashmolean Museum, University of Oxford (*Ashmolean Image Library, 01/02/2025*).\n- **Slide 4 / 4**: Sumerian King List. © Ashmolean Museum, University of Oxford (*Ashmolean Image Library, 02/01/2024*).",
